sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>Argo
    participant Pod as Pipeline Step Pod
    participant S3 as S3/Minio<br/>9000/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission
    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    OAuth->>API: Forward HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL Auth
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>Service Account
    API->>MLMD: Record metadata (optional)<br/>gRPC mTLS
    API-->>User: Pipeline Created

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution
    WFC->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>Service Account
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow Created Event
    WFC->>K8s: Create Pipeline Step Pod<br/>Service Account
    K8s-->>Pod: Pod Started
    Pod->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>S3 Credentials
    Pod->>Pod: Execute pipeline step
    Pod->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>S3 Credentials
    Pod->>MLMD: Record artifact lineage<br/>gRPC mTLS (optional)
    Pod-->>K8s: Pod Completed

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: Status Persistence
    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow Status<br/>Service Account
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow Status Update
    PA->>DB: Sync execution status<br/>MySQL Auth

    Note over User,DB: Flow 4: Artifact Access
    User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/artifacts/(id)<br/>OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS
    OAuth->>API: Forward Bearer Token
    API->>S3: Generate signed URL<br/>S3 Credentials
    API-->>User: Signed URL (60s TTL)<br/>HTTPS

    Note over User,DB: Flow 5: MLMD Metadata Query (Optional)
    User->>Route: gRPC MetadataStoreService<br/>OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS
    OAuth->>MLMD: Forward gRPC<br/>mTLS (optional)
    MLMD->>DB: Query artifact lineage<br/>MySQL Auth
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage data
    MLMD-->>User: Metadata response
